                'Me.WorkSets("sca100_f10").DeleteRow()   '특정Workset을 삭제

            Case MenuType.New
                Me.New_Form()
                'Me.WorkSets("mmb100_g10").AddNew()  '특정Workset 신규처리

            Case MenuType.Print
                ' Me.Print()

            Case Else
